summary:
Incoming student to the Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam to study Artificial Intelligence. I am particularly interested in understanding the relationship between technology and society, focusing on how you can plan for and mitigate the unintended consequences technology can bring.

I have experience in corporate strategy and business development, from creating investor pitch decks to building financial models.
